episodes.title: Archer Vice: White Elephant
episodes.plot: After ISIS headquarters is raided by FBI Agents, Archer and Lana work to break out the crew while Mallory works on a deal to get them all free.

episodes.title: Archer Vice: A Kiss While Dying
episodes.plot: Archer, Pam and Lana travel to Miami to visit some old friends. It's a fondue party!

episodes.title: Archer Vice: A Debt of Honor
episodes.plot: Pam gets targeted for death by the Yakuza while the group continues to dig their way out of financial trouble.

episodes.title: Archer Vice: House Call
episodes.plot: Archer has to stage an intervention for Pam that gets derailed by an unwanted guest.

episodes.title: Archer Vice: Southbound and Down
episodes.plot: Malory buys a bus and takes everyone on a road trip. Put that hammer down and give it hell.

episodes.title: Archer Vice: Baby Shower
episodes.plot: Archer and Pam try to get Kenny Loggins to play at Lana's baby shower and wind up in a zone of danger.

episodes.title: Archer Vice: Smugglers' Blues
episodes.plot: Archer travels to Columbia on a secret mission that becomes not so secret after he gets drunk.

episodes.title: Archer Vice: The Rules of Extraction
episodes.plot: Archer, Ray, and Cyril raft down a crocodile-filled river while Lana and Pam plan a spa day for Malory.

episodes.title: Archer Vice: On the Carpet
episodes.plot: Archer avoids crash landing in a dangerous swamp only to come face-to-face with a shady arms dealer (Christian Slater).

episodes.title: Archer Vice: Palace Intrigue - Part I
episodes.plot: Archer and the rest of the ISIS gang are the guests of Gustavo Calderon and his wife Juliana. Calderon is a big fan of Cherlene but Juliana is a bigger fan of Archer.

episodes.title: Archer Vice: Palace Intrigue: Part II
episodes.plot: Archer tries to keep his fling with the dictator's wife a secret while Krieger bonds with his clone-brothers.

episodes.title: Archer Vice: Filibuster
episodes.plot: Cyril becomes the new president of San Marcos, Cherlene becomes the first lady of country music, and Archer becomes a resistance fighter.

episodes.title: Archer Vice: Arrival/Departure
episodes.plot: While Lana is trying to give birth to her baby, it turns out that the whole "cocaine-case" was a secret agreement between Malory and the CIA.
